originalSql:
SELECT 
    a.name AS actor_name,
    t.title AS movie_title,
    t.production_year,
    STRING_AGG(DISTINCT k.keyword, ',') AS keywords,
    STRING_AGG(DISTINCT c.kind, ',') AS company_types,
    STRING_AGG(DISTINCT r.role, ',') AS roles
FROM 
    aka_name a
JOIN 
    cast_info ci ON a.person_id = ci.person_id
JOIN 
    title t ON ci.movie_id = t.id
LEFT JOIN 
    movie_keyword mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id
LEFT JOIN 
    keyword k ON mk.keyword_id = k.id
LEFT JOIN 
    movie_companies mc ON t.id = mc.movie_id
LEFT JOIN 
    company_type c ON mc.company_type_id = c.id
LEFT JOIN 
    role_type r ON ci.role_id = r.id
WHERE 
    a.name LIKE '%Smith%'     
    AND t.production_year >= 2000  
GROUP BY 
    a.name, t.title, t.production_year
ORDER BY 
    t.production_year DESC, a.name

FROM (SELECT "t0"."id", "t0"."person_id", "t0"."name", "t0"."imdb_index", "t0"."name_pcode_cf", "t0"."name_pcode_nf", "t0"."surname_pcode", "t0"."md5sum", "cast_info"."id" AS "id0", "cast_info"."person_id" AS "person_id0", "cast_info"."movie_id", "cast_info"."person_role_id", "cast_info"."note", "cast_info"."nr_order", "cast_info"."role_id", "t1"."id" AS "id1", "t1"."title", "t1"."imdb_index" AS "imdb_index0", "t1"."kind_id", "t1"."production_year", "t1"."imdb_id", "t1"."phonetic_code", "t1"."episode_of_id", "t1"."season_nr", "t1"."episode_nr", "t1"."series_years", "t1"."md5sum" AS "md5sum0", "movie_keyword"."id" AS "id2", "movie_keyword"."movie_id" AS "movie_id0", "movie_keyword"."keyword_id"
FROM "cast_info"
INNER JOIN (SELECT *

WHERE "name" LIKE '%Smith%') AS "t0" ON "cast_info"."person_id" = "t0"."person_id"
INNER JOIN ("movie_keyword" RIGHT JOIN (SELECT *

LEFT JOIN "role_type" ON "t2"."role_id" = "role_type"."id"
